summary: You like High Elves? But you think all the Vanilla Presets are ugly? Well then this is the perfect File for YOU! Juno, a female High Elve.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=3]
[img]http://img5.fotos-hochladen.net/uploads/junor4lkixnejz.png[/img]

First of all this Preset requires [/size][b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url]! 
[/b][size=3]I think its pretty obvious what this File is, but just incase: This File is a Preset which you can load via. Racemenu in the charactor creation menu. This Preset is for the High Elve Race [b]only[/b]. The only way the Preset is gonna look the same in ur game is to install the required Mods. 
Please do not redistribute my Preset![/size][/center][center][size=5][u][b][img]http://i.epvpimg.com/tInOc.png[/img]
Required Mods: [/b][/u]
[/size]
-The Eyes of Beauty by LogRaam
-CBBE body Mod by Caliente
-SG Hair Pack 268 by HelloSanta

All up-to-date versions of the Mods above should work just fine. (15.07.15)
Thanks to every of the above mod creators for their awesome work![/center][center][b][u][size=5][img]http://i.epvpimg.com/tInOc.png[/img]
Installation: 

[/size][/u][/b][size=3]Just extract Juno.jslot to Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets

[/size][size=5][b][u]Unistallation: 
[/u][/b][/size][size=3]
I dont understand why anyone would ask that but mkay.

Remove Juno.jslot from Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets[/size][/center]
author: Rexidexi
